---
import Base from '@/layouts/Base.astro';
import Section from '@/components/Section.astro';

const title = 'BibleWise - Support';
const description = 'Support and help for BibleWise - Bible Quiz & Trivia App';
---

<Base head={{ title, description }}>
	<Section>
		<article class="prose prose-gray dark:prose-invert max-w-4xl mx-auto">
			<h1>BibleWise Support</h1>
			<p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
				Get help with BibleWise - Bible Quiz & Trivia
			</p>

			<h2>Getting Started</h2>

			<h3>How do I play?</h3>
			<p>
				BibleWise offers three game modes:
			</p>
			<ol>
				<li><strong>Levels</strong> - Progress through 20 increasingly challenging levels covering the entire Bible. Earn stars to unlock new content.</li>
				<li><strong>Daily Challenge</strong> - Answer fresh questions every day and build your streak for bonus rewards.</li>
				<li><strong>Timed Mode</strong> - Race against a 60-second clock and answer as many questions as you can.</li>
			</ol>

			<h3>How do stars work?</h3>
			<p>
				Stars are earned across all three game modes and contribute to your total star count. Stars unlock new levels and track your progress:
			</p>
			<ul>
				<li><strong>Levels</strong> - Earn up to 3 stars per level based on your score</li>
				<li><strong>Daily Challenge</strong> - Stars accumulate each day you play</li>
				<li><strong>Timed Mode</strong> - Earn up to 3 stars based on your best performance</li>
			</ul>

			<h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

			<h3>How do hints work?</h3>
			<p>
				Hints help you with tough questions by eliminating incorrect answers. You start with a few free hints and can earn more through:
			</p>
			<ul>
				<li>Achieving streak milestones in Daily Challenge</li>
				<li>Getting a perfect score in Daily Challenge</li>
				<li>Purchasing hint packs from the Shop</li>
			</ul>

			<h3>How do streaks work?</h3>
			<p>
				Complete the Daily Challenge each day to build your streak. Hit milestones for bonus rewards:
			</p>
			<ul>
				<li><strong>3 days</strong> - Bonus stars and hints</li>
				<li><strong>7 days</strong> - Larger bonus</li>
				<li><strong>14 days</strong> - Even bigger bonus</li>
				<li><strong>30 days</strong> - Major milestone reward</li>
				<li><strong>Every 7 days after 30</strong> - Recurring rewards</li>
			</ul>

			<h3>What question packs are available?</h3>
			<p>
				In addition to the base questions, you can unlock:
			</p>
			<ul>
				<li><strong>Prophets Pack</strong> - 100+ questions about the Prophets</li>
				<li><strong>Gospels Pack</strong> - 100+ questions about the Gospels</li>
				<li><strong>All Questions Bundle</strong> - Unlocks all current and future question packs</li>
			</ul>

			<h3>How do I restore my purchases?</h3>
			<p>
				If you've previously made purchases in BibleWise:
			</p>
			<ol>
				<li>Open the Shop from the main menu</li>
				<li>Scroll to the bottom and tap "Restore Purchases"</li>
				<li>Sign in with the same Apple ID you used for the purchase</li>
				<li>Your purchases will be restored automatically</li>
			</ol>

			<h2>Troubleshooting</h2>

			<h3>The app is crashing</h3>
			<p>
				Try these troubleshooting steps:
			</p>
			<ol>
				<li>Force quit the app and restart it</li>
				<li>Restart your device</li>
				<li>Check for app updates in the App Store</li>
				<li>Ensure you have enough storage space</li>
				<li>If issues persist, contact support with your device model and iOS version</li>
			</ol>

			<h3>My progress was lost</h3>
			<p>
				BibleWise stores your progress locally on your device. If your progress was lost:
			</p>
			<ul>
				<li>Ensure you haven't deleted and reinstalled the app</li>
				<li>Check that you have enough storage space on your device</li>
				<li>Purchased content can always be restored via "Restore Purchases" in the Shop</li>
			</ul>

			<h3>A purchase didn't go through</h3>
			<p>
				If a purchase appears to have failed:
			</p>
			<ol>
				<li>Check your internet connection</li>
				<li>Try tapping "Restore Purchases" in the Shop</li>
				<li>Verify the charge in your Apple ID purchase history</li>
				<li>If charged but not received, contact Apple Support for a refund</li>
			</ol>

			<h2>Contact Support</h2>
			<p>
				If you need additional help or want to report a bug, please reach out through the App Store where you downloaded the app. You can also leave a review with your feedback.
			</p>

			<h2>Feature Requests</h2>
			<p>
				Have an idea for new questions or features? We'd love to hear from you! Please share your suggestions through App Store reviews.
			</p>

			<h2>Leave a Review</h2>
			<p>
				Is BibleWise helping you grow in your knowledge of Scripture? Please consider leaving a review on the App Store. Your feedback helps us improve and helps others discover the app!
			</p>

			<div class="mt-12 p-6 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg">
				<p class="text-sm text-center text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
					<a href="/" class="hover:text-orange-600 transition-colors">&larr; Back to tskulbru.com</a> |
					<a href="/apps/biblewise-privacy" class="hover:text-orange-600 transition-colors">Privacy Policy</a> |
					<a href="https://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/itunes/dev/stdeula/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:text-orange-600 transition-colors">Terms of Use (EULA)</a>
				</p>
			</div>
		</article>
	</Section>
</Base>
